examples.en: He watched a spider spinning its web.
Our wheels were spinning on the ice.
I tried to stand up but the room was spinning.
I felt like I was just spinning my wheels trying to make him understand.
The spinning turbine creates a vacuum.
The spinning motion gives a stability to the axis of rotation.
The car slid sideways, its rear wheels spinning.
The children were dizzy after spinning in circles.
The impact of the blow sent me spinning like a top.
I was pouring with sweat, and my head was spinning.
The administration is relentlessly spinning the war.
A spinning maelstrom of rain swept around the mountain.
The car was spinning along nicely when suddenly the engine stopped.
